\c 12 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 12\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Dubbii Namaa Fi Dubbii Waaqayyoo (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun toora saddeettaffaa irratti faarfatame; faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, namni siif of kenne hin jiru, ati nu gargaari! Warri amanamoon ilmaan namootaa gidduudhaa badaniiru'o.
\m \bd 2\bd* namoonni adduma addaan walii isaaniitti soba in dubbatu, afaaniin namatti kuuluudhaaf garaa walaallammiidhaan in dubbatu;
\m \bd 3\bd* hidhii sobaan namatti kuulu hundumaa, arraba jajuu gurguddaa dubbatus, gooftichi haa kukkutu.
\m \bd 4\bd* Namoonni, ''Nuyi arraba keenyaan humna in godhanna, hidhiin keenya nutti jira, eenyutu nu irratti gooftaa ta'a ree?'' in jedhu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waaqayyo gooftaan immoo, ''Warri jara gadadamoo irratti humnaan ka'an waan jiraniif, warri wanta barbaachisaa dhabanis waan aadaniif, amma ani ka'uufan jedha, gargaarsa isaan hawwanis akka argatan nan godhaaf'' in jedha.
\m \bd 6\bd* Dubbiin Waaqayyoo dubbii qullaa'aa dha, inni akka meetii iddoo ibiddaatti si'a torba baqfamee qullaa'ee ti;
\m \bd 7\bd* yaa Waaqayyo, ati nu irra in golgita, dhaloota kanattiis yeroo hundumaa nu eegda.
\m \bd 8\bd* Amalli gadheen ilmaan namootaa gidduutti akkuma ol ka'aa adeemu, warri jal'oonni gara hundumaan caqasaa yoo marsan iyyuu, ati nu eegda.
